room_title: Escape room "Amnesia" by Escape 605 in Sioux Falls
room_address: 3718 S Westport Ave, Sioux Falls, SD 57106
room_description:
Fabulous Las Vegas. The biggest party of all. It was a great night, wasn’t it? Shame you can’t remember a thing. What the hell happened? How did we all get here?
Security is showing up in one hour to clear us out because of all the trouble we caused last night. Does the slogan “What happens in Vegas stays in Vegas” apply to us?
Players must be 18 or older.
